data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to your dream home! This captivating two-story residence boasts 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and an array of luxurious features that define modern comfort. As you cross the threshold, the grandeur of high ceilings sets the tone for an inviting living space. The living room beckons with a warm embrace, creating the perfect ambiance for relaxation and entertaining. Flow seamlessly from the living room to the dining room, ensuring that conversations can continue effortlessly. The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring wood cabinets, large windows with treatments that invite natural light, an Eating Space, and modern updates, including a convenient double oven. This home offers both functionality and flexibility with a loft and a downstairs office, providing versatile spaces for work or leisure. Ascend to the primary bedroom, a spacious retreat offering tranquility and privacy. The attached bathroom is a spa-like oasis, complete with a glass walk-in shower and Dual Sinks. The two additional bedrooms are charming and thoughtfully designed, featuring ceiling fans and just the right amount of closet space to meet your storage needs. The home also includes a dedicated space for entertainment and fitness enthusiasts, with a billiard game area and a gym space. Step outside through the inviting doors to the covered, enclosed, spacious patio area perfect for grilling and outdoor dining. perfect for year-round enjoyment, providing a delightful space for relaxation and gatherings. As part of a vibrant community, residents enjoy access to a range of amenities, including a community pool for refreshing dips on sunny days and a playground for outdoor recreation. Embrace the lifestyle you deserve in this meticulously crafted and well-appointed home. Schedule a tour today and experience the epitome of modern living!
